voices.mp3Text: The Light guides me on my quest.

I am the keeper of the light!

I bring a light to scour your soul!
Do not fear the light—fear me!

voices.mp3Text: Out of Chaos, order is imposed.
voices.name: Chaos Knight

voices.mp3Text: You'll not threaten the light, Chaos Knight.
voices.name: Chaos Knight

voices.mp3Text: Not while I am keeper of the light!
voices.name: Chaos Knight

voices.mp3Text: Night Stalker, I bring you into the light.
voices.name: Night Stalker

voices.mp3Text: You were as old as the first day, but I am as old as the first light.
voices.name: Night Stalker

voices.mp3Text: Here's light in your eye. Eh heh heh heh.
voices.name: Night Stalker

voices.mp3Text: They said not even light can escape you. They lied.
voices.name: Enigma

voices.mp3Text: Light is wasted on the eyeless one.
voices.name: Faceless Void

voices.mp3Text: Ancient you were, dead you are.
voices.name: Ancient Apparition

voices.mp3Text: First blood! My quest begins auspiciously!
Surely there was blood before that one? I can't quite remember.
I'll expect you to be on your best behavior, Chaos Knight.
voices.name: Chaos Knight

voices.mp3Text: Well, Night Stalker, the daytime's not as bad as all that, is it?
voices.name: Night Stalker

voices.mp3Text: My Lady of Pain, I adore you.
voices.name: Queen of Pain

voices.mp3Text: Youth before age, my dear. Please, you go first.
voices.name: Enchantress

voices.mp3Text: Lady Mirana, the honor is mine.
voices.name: Mirana

voices.mp3Text: Dear Luna, tis the moon that reflects your light.
voices.name: Luna

voices.mp3Text: Ah, to share the field of battle with such beauty is an honor.
voices.name: Phantom Assassin

voices.mp3Text: Drow Ranger, I am scarce worthy of your presence.
voices.name: Drow Ranger

voices.mp3Text: Mother that you are, you have my great respect.
voices.name: Broodmother

voices.mp3Text: Forgive me, my lady, your beauty makes me blush.
voices.name: Vengeful Spirit

voices.mp3Text: You bring a bloom of youth to these pallid cheeks, my lady.
voices.name: Crystal Maiden

voices.mp3Text: Would that my whiskers were dark again, I would ride out on any quest you named.
voices.name: Naga Siren

voices.mp3Text: Ah, sweet Lina, if I did not carry this light I would carry a torch for you.
voices.name: Lina

voices.mp3Text: I know you cannot see it now, my dear girl, but I was a young gallant once.
voices.name: Templar Assassin

voices.mp3Text: Spectre, I'm sure in your world you are known as a great beauty.
voices.name: Spectre

voices.mp3Text: It is my heart's dearest wish to acquit myself nobly in your sight, good lady Medusa.
voices.name: Medusa

voices.mp3Text: A heavy purse makes a light heart.
